        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/29462902" target="_blank" rel="noopener">理解Hartree-Fork</a></p><h1 id="Hartree-Forks近似"><a href="#Hartree-Forks近似" class="headerlink" title="Hartree-Forks近似"></a>Hartree-Forks近似</h1><script type="math/tex; mode=display">E_{\mathrm{HF}}=\sum_{i=1}^{N} H_{i}+\frac{1}{2}\sum_{i, j=1}^{N}\left( J_{ij}-K_{ij}\right) \tag{1.1}</script><p>其中</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\quad H_{i}=\int \psi_{i}^{*}(\mathbf{x})\left[-\frac{1}{2} \nabla^{2}+v(\mathbf{x})\right] \psi_{i}(\mathbf{x}) d \mathbf{x}</script><p>Coulomb integrals:</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">J_{i j}=\iint \psi_{i}\left(\mathbf{x}_{1}\right) \psi_{i}^{*}\left(\mathbf{x}_{1}\right) \frac{1}{r_{12}} \psi_{j}^{*}\left(\mathbf{x}_{2}\right) \psi_{j}\left(\mathbf{x}_{2}\right) d \mathbf{x}_{1} d \mathbf{x}_{2}</script><p>Exchange integrals:</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">K_{i j}=\iint \psi_{i}^{*}\left(\mathbf{x}_{1}\right) \psi_{j}\left(\mathbf{x}_{1}\right) \frac{1}{r_{12}} \psi_{i}\left(\mathbf{x}_{2}\right) \psi_{j}^{*}\left(\mathbf{x}_{2}\right) d \mathbf{x}_{1} d \mathbf{x}_{2}</script>]]></content>
      
      
