      <title>第一章量子态的描述</title>
      <link href="/2020/09/28/%E9%AB%98%E9%87%8F%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0/"/>
      <url>/2020/09/28/%E9%AB%98%E9%87%8F%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="第一章：量子态的描述"><a href="#第一章：量子态的描述" class="headerlink" title="第一章：量子态的描述"></a>第一章：量子态的描述</h1><h2 id="1-2密度矩阵"><a href="#1-2密度矩阵" class="headerlink" title="1.2密度矩阵"></a>1.2密度矩阵</h2><h3 id="1-2-1密度算符与密度矩阵"><a href="#1-2-1密度算符与密度矩阵" class="headerlink" title="1.2.1密度算符与密度矩阵"></a>1.2.1密度算符与密度矩阵</h3><p><font color = "red" face="黑体">投影算符</font>:</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">P_n = |n\rangle \langle n|</script><p><font color = "red" face="黑体">密度算符</font>：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\rho(t)=|\psi(t)\rangle\langle\psi(t)|</script><p>采取F表象时与量子态$|\psi\rangle$对应的密度算符可以表现为<font color = "red" face="黑体">矩阵形式</font>：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\rho_{nn'}(t) = \langle n|\rho(t)|n'\rangle=C_n(t)C_{n'}^*(t)</script><p>另一种表达形式</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned}\rho &=|\psi(t)\rangle\langle\psi(t)|=\sum_{nn^{\prime}}| n\rangle\langle n | \psi(t)\rangle\langle\psi(t) | n^{\prime}  \rangle\langle n^{\prime}  | \\&=\sum_{nn^{\prime}} C_{n}(t) C_{n}^{*}(t)|n\rangle\langle n^{\prime}|=\sum_{nn^{\prime}} \rho_{nn^{\prime}}(t)  | n\rangle\langle n^{\prime}  |\end{aligned}</script><p><font color = "red" face="黑体">力学量的密度矩阵计算方法：</font></p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\langle G\rangle=tr(\rho G)=tr(G\rho)</script><p><font color = "red" face="黑体">密度算符的演化：</font></p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\frac{d}{dt}\rho(t)=\frac{1}{i\hbar}[H,\rho(t)]</script><p>对比Heisenberg表象下 力学量的演化：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\frac{d}{dt}F=\frac{1}{i\hbar}[F,H]+\frac{\partial F}{\partial t}</script><p>在能量表征下</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{array}{c}\rho_{n n^{\prime}}(t)=\rho_{nn^{\prime}}(0) \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i\omega }_{nn^{\prime}}} \\\omega_{n n^{\prime}}=\left(E_{n}-E_{n^{\prime}}\right) / \hbar\end{array}</script><p>即非对角元$\rho_{nn’}(t)(n\ne n’)$以角频率$\omega_{nn’}$震荡，而对角元不随时间变化</p><h3 id="1-2-2混合态的密度矩阵"><a href="#1-2-2混合态的密度矩阵" class="headerlink" title="1.2.2混合态的密度矩阵"></a>1.2.2混合态的密度矩阵</h3><p><font color="red" face="黑体">混合态密度算符：</font></p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\rho = \sum_{k}p_k|\psi_k\rangle\langle\psi_k| = \sum_k p_k\rho_k</script><p><font color="red" face="黑体">混合态密度矩阵：</font></p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\rho_{nn\prime} = \sum_k p_k C_n^k C_{n\prime}^{k*}</script><p><font color="red" face="黑体">布居：</font>$\rho_{nn}$称为混合态下量子态$|n\rangle$的布居（population）</p><p><font color="red" face="黑体">相干：</font>非对角元$\rho_{nn’}\ne0$称为相干（coherence）<br>$\rho_{nn’}=0$则$|n\rangle$和$|n’\rangle$不相干</p><h3 id="1-2-3-复合体系的子体系，约化密度矩阵"><a href="#1-2-3-复合体系的子体系，约化密度矩阵" class="headerlink" title="1.2.3 复合体系的子体系，约化密度矩阵"></a>1.2.3 复合体系的子体系，约化密度矩阵</h3>]]></content>
      
      
      
