        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="这是我的第一篇文章"><a href="#这是我的第一篇文章" class="headerlink" title="这是我的第一篇文章"></a>这是我的第一篇文章</h1><p>今天呢基于Markdown和hexo写了我第一篇博客。首先呢是搭建和部署blog，我是参照<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty?from=search&amp;seid=14737339664452128870" target="_blank" rel="noopener">视频手把手教你从0开始搭建自己的个人博客 |无坑版视频教程| hexo</a>弄的。然后是Markdown的使用，主要参考的是<a href="https://www.limfx.pro/ReadArticle/57/yi-zhong-xie-zuo-de-xin-fang-fa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">文章Markdown写作</a>，对应<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1si4y1472o?from=search&amp;seid=1957919730677943135" target="_blank" rel="noopener">视频：教你Markdown+VSCODE实现最完美流畅写作体验</a>。但是hexo中有非常多的Tag，他们可以是实现更为丰富的效果。主要可以参考<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo官方手册</a>和我的<a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">主题Next的手册</a>。这篇文章就当做我使用hexo，创建博客的日志。</p><h1 id="Markdown-基本语法"><a href="#Markdown-基本语法" class="headerlink" title="Markdown 基本语法"></a>Markdown 基本语法</h1><div class="tabs" id="fourth-unique-name"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a href="#fourth-unique-name-1">代码</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#fourth-unique-name-2">渲染效果</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="fourth-unique-name-1"><p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">换行：这几个字后面有两个空格  </span><br><span class="line">然后换了一行，但是还是一段</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">换段：换了一段</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**强调**</span>  <span class="emphasis">*斜体*</span> </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>这是列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">   1. </span>哈哈哈</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">插入图片：</span><br><span class="line">![](https://ss2.bdstatic.com/70cFvnSh<span class="emphasis">_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=2598969791,1832410843&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0.jpghttps://ss2.bdstatic.com/70cFvnSh_</span>Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=2598969791,1832410843&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0.jpg)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*小兔子*</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">插入表格：</span><br><span class="line">| jjj    | dfdfs |</span><br><span class="line"> | ------ | :---: |</span><br><span class="line"> | dfasdf | sdfas |</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">大公式</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\lim_&#123;x \to \infty&#125;\frac&#123;sin(t)&#125;&#123;x&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是一个公式 $\lim\limits_&#123;0 \to \infty&#125;f(x)$</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">化学公式：$\ce&#123;N2 + 3H2 <span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">=</span>&gt;</span></span>T[<span class="string">高温、加压</span>][<span class="symbol">催化剂</span>] 2NH3&#125;$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>代码块</p><p>```python</p><p>import tensorflow as tf</p><p>```</p><p>关于公式的渲染要参考<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/68e6f82d88b7" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这篇文章</a>，因为hexo自带的公式渲染器并不好使。最后要到主题的设置文件中，改为mathjax: true</p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="fourth-unique-name-2"><p>换行：这几个字后面有两个空格<br>然后换了一行，但是还是一段</p><p>换段：换了一段</p><p><strong>强调</strong>  <em>斜体</em></p><ol><li>这是列表<ol><li>哈哈哈</li></ol></li></ol><p><img src="https://ss2.bdstatic.com/70cFvnSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=2598969791,1832410843&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0.jpghttps://ss2.bdstatic.com/70cFvnSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=2598969791,1832410843&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0.jpg" alt=""><br><em>小兔子</em></p><div class="table-container"><table><thead><tr><th>jjj</th><th style="text-align:center">dfdfs</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>dfasdf</td><td style="text-align:center">sdfas</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>大公式  </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\lim_{x \to \infty}\frac{sin(t)}{x}</script><p>这是一个公式 $\lim\limits_{0 \to \infty}f(x)$</p><p>化学公式$\ce{N2 + 3H2 &lt;=&gt;T[高温、加压][催化剂] 2NH3}$</p><p>代码块  </p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> tensorflow <span class="keyword">as</span> tf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div></div><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
